text: Services and Deliverables
Services

The Supplier shall provide behavioural data analytics services to the Customer as a proof of concept (POC), comprising:(a) receiving from the Customer a dataset containing behavioural signals relating to the Customer's end users (the Input Data);(b) processing the Input Data using the Supplier's proprietary behavioural analytics model to identify behavioural patterns, cluster end users into profile types and predict future behaviours and outcomes for those profile types; and(c) returning to the Customer the Input Data enriched with the outputs of the Supplier's behavioural analysis (the Deliverables).The Supplier shall determine the methodology for performing the behavioural analytics in its sole discretion. The Customer acknowledges that the Services are provided on an "as is" basis for evaluation purposes only and without any warranty as to accuracy, fitness for purpose or suitability for any particular use.
